# 🚀 Day 66/90 – Display the Uploaded Report Details

Welcome to **Day 66!** 🎉

Yesterday, we built an upload progress screen.

Today, we'll make the app feel more realistic by showing a **Report Details** screen after the upload completes.

In a real application, this screen will eventually display data extracted from OCR and AI. For now, we'll use sample values so the app flow is complete.

---

# 🎯 Today's Goal

After today's work, the flow will be:

```text
Dashboard
    ↓
Upload Report
    ↓
Select PDF/Image
    ↓
