# 🚀 A Small Change to Our Roadmap

Originally, I planned to spend a few more days polishing the upload process before introducing OCR.

Instead, I think a better path for your goal is:

* **Day 67–69:** Integrate OCR so the app extracts text from uploaded reports.
* **Day 70–72:** Convert extracted text into structured health values (Hemoglobin, HbA1c, Vitamin D, etc.).
* **After that:** Connect AI to explain those values in plain language.

This keeps every new feature moving the app closer to a working MVP that someone could actually use.
